    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2019 Lexus RX 350 in Eminent White Pearl. This vehicle has been garage-kept and serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships, with a full folder of maintenance records included. Mechanically, it is in excellent shape, providing the smooth and quiet ride Lexus is known for. The exterior retains a deep gloss, though I want to be transparent about two small, professionally touched-up stone chips on the front bumper and a minor scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel rim. Inside, the Parchment leather interior is smoke-free and pristine, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. All tech features\u2014including the navigation system, heated/ventilated seats, and premium sound system\u2014are fully operational. The tires were replaced last year and have significant tread life remaining. This is a reliable, high-end SUV that has been cared for with pride and is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
